page.title: 15TRAFFIC SURVEY (PART 2)
page.content: In the same traffic census we noted car registration plates,coming from Scarborough.Results are as follows: From London.16 From Yorkshire.178 (104 from Leeds, 34 from York) From East Anglia. 12 From Scotland.9 From the North West.29 From the North East.20 From Central England,32 From Western England.17 From the South Coast.17 From Humberside. 26 From Wales.9 From Ireland.4 From Abroad.6 Personal Number plates. 3 TOTAL 378. (Number plates only give an accurate account of where the vehicles were first registered).
